{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">An Exile's Desert Adventure</h2>Explore this psychedelic and dangerous desert. Gather materials, change the terrain, and build shelters. Forge weapons and defeat increasingly powerful enemies. Explore the ruins all over the map, collect them, and finally rely on the power of the witch and witch to rebuild the ancient city.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399140/extras/travel.gif?t=1682738989\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Completely Free sandbox</h2>In the game, you will get a powerful force of nature, which can change the terrain at will. You can dig deep ditches to protect your homeland, or you can build mountains to look far away. You can even dig water sources and turn the desert into an oasis.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399140/extras/build.gif?t=1682738989\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Reconstruction Of the Ancient City Of Lan</h2>During the adventure, you will come across various lost ruins in the ancient city of Lan, and try to collect them. After giving the relic crystal to the witch, she will give you more powerful power, and finally be able to shake the ancient city walls and buildings and rebuild the ancient city!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399140/extras/shake.gif?t=1682738989\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build A Shelter</h2>Build your own cabin, snooze around the fire and grill raw meat. Chat with the witch to learn about the past of this desert.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399140/extras/shelter.gif?t=1682738989\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master Fighting Skills</h2>Different weapons have different skills, master them proficiently. Collect materials and build them stronger.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstati